message: Let's split it 50/50, a fair start!
You started high, I'll start low, let's meet in the middle
You went too low, I'll meet you in the middle
You met me in the middle, I'll move up
You went up, I'll meet you again
You met me again, I'll make a strong move now
You're getting aggressive, I'll try to counter
You tried to counter, I'll push for the majority
You're getting too greedy, I'll try to salvage
You're trying to salvage, I'll take the last stand
You're making a last stand, I'll try to negotiate
It's my last chance, I'll take almost all
